Reasoning: 
1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with spatial spectrum estimation and interference suppression, which are related to information theory. 
2. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - The paper proposes a hybrid analog-and-digital beamforming scheme for interference reduction, which is a signal processing technique. 
3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses interference reduction in wireless communication, which is related to networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with improving the receive quality of the desired signal, which is related to multimedia applications. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a robust hybrid beamforming algorithm using the conditional expectation of DOA, which is a machine learning technique.
